- `read_events_lenient`: reads full file, parses JSON on every line (also full scan)
- `read_tail`: reads full file into string, but only keeps last N lines without parsing all of them as JSON
- `read_tail_events`: calls `read_tail` (reads full file, keeps last N lines), then parses only those N lines as JSON

